wp:list --><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>The concept</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Imagine arriving in a city like Paris or Mumbai and somebody is already waiting for you. Imagine that instead of going to eat at the place recommended by the guidebook, someone shows you their favorite restaurant. Imagine the experience staying as a personal guest of your new friend rather than sleeping in an impersonal hotel room.<strong>DirtyRoad </strong>makes it possible.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>How is it organised?</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Dreaming alone is not enough. That\'s why we have founded<a href=\"https://www.bewelcome.org/wiki/BeVolunteer\">BeVolunteer</a>, a non-profit organisation registered in Rennes, France. Through BeVolunteer\'s official statutes, we provide a basis for democratic decision making, financial transparency and information security so that we can protect our members and manage the project BeWelcome effectively.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>You like the idea? Get active!</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Join one of our teams: Share the work, commitment and fun! We are currently looking for:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:list -->\n<ul>\n<li>Developers</li>\n<li>Designers</li>\n<li>Testers</li>\n<li>Member Support</li>\n<li>Translators</li>\n<li>Local volunteers</li>\n</ul>\n<!-- /wp:list --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Thank You!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Your opinion, please!</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We are constantly working on the improvement of <strong>DirtyRoad </strong>. If you have a suggestion, please<a href=\"https://www.bewelcome.org/about/feedback?IdCategory=7\">let us know</a>.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','About','','publish','closed','closed','','about','','','2021-05-23 07:00:02','2021-05-23 07:00:02','',0,'http://loca