 do we use ?</h3><div>Essential: Some cookies are essential for you to be able to experience the full functionality of our site. They allow us to maintain user sessions and prevent any security threats. They do not collect or store any personal information. For example, these cookies allow you to log-in to your account and add products to your basket, and checkout securely.\n\nStatistics: These cookies store information like the number of visitors to the website, the number of unique visitors, which pages of the website have been visited, the source of the visit, etc. These data help us understand and analyze how well the website performs and where it needs improvement.\n\nMarketing: Our website displays advertisements. These cookies are used to personalize the advertisements that we show to you so that they are meaningful to you. These cookies also help us keep track of the efficiency of these ad campaigns.\nThe information stored in these cookies may also be used by the third-party ad providers to show you ads on other websites on the browser as well.\n\nFunctional: TThese are the cookies that help certain non-essential functionalities on our website. These functionalities include embedding content like videos or sharing content of the website on social media platforms.\n\nPreferences: These cookies help us store your settings and browsing preferences like language preferences so that you have a better and efficient experience on future visits to the website.\n[cookie_audit columns=\"cookie,description\" heading=\"The below list details the cookies used in our website.\"]</div><h3>How can I control the cookie preferences ?</h3><div>Should you decide to change your preferences later through your browsing session, you can click on the \"Privacy &amp; Cookie Policy\" tab on your screen. This will display the consent notice again enabling you to change your preferences or withdraw your consent entirely.\n\nIn addition to this, different browsers provide different methods to block and delete cookies used by websites. You can change the settings of your browser to block/delete the cookies. To find out more about how to manage and delete cookies, visit wikipedia.org, www.allaboutcookies.org.</div></div>','Cookie Policy','','draft','closed','closed','','','','','2021-05-23 06:56:32','0000-00-00 00:00:00','',0,'http://localhost/dirtyroad/?page_id=216',0,'page','',0),(217,1,'2021-05-23 06:59:24','2021-05-23 06:59:24','<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>The idea</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The Idea has been conceived and developed by:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li><strong>Luis Mandel</strong></li><li><strong>Andrs Lopez</strong></li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>The concept</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Imagine arriving in a city like Paris or Mumbai and somebody is already waiting for you. Imagine that instead of going to eat at the place recommended by the guidebook, someone shows you their favorite restaurant. Imagine the experience staying as a personal guest of your new friend rather than sleeping in an impersonal hotel room.<strong>DirtyRoad</strong>makes it possible.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>How is it organised?</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Dreaming alone is not enough. That\'s why we have founded&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.bewelcome.org/wiki/BeVolunteer\">BeVolunteer</a>, a non-profit organisation registered in Rennes, France. Through BeVolunteer\'s official statutes, we provide a basis for democratic decision making, financial transparency and information security so that we can protect our members and manage the project BeWelcome effectively.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>You like the idea? Get active!</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Join one of our teams: Share the work, commitment and fun! We are currently looking for:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Developers</li><li>Designers</li><li>Testers</li><li>Member Support</li><li>Translators</li><li>Local volunteers</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Thank You!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Your opinion, please!</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We are constantly working on the improvement of <strong>DirtyRoad</strong>. If you have a suggestion, please<a href=\"https://www.bewelcome.org/about/feedback?IdCategory=7\">let us know</a>.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','About','','inherit','closed','closed','','65-revision-v1','','','2021-05-23 06:59:24','2021-05-23 06:59:24','',65,'http://localhost/dirtyroad/?p=217',0,'revision','',0),(218,1,'2021-05-23 06:59:24','2021-05-23 06:59:24','<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>The idea</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The Idea has been conceived and developed by:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li><strong>Luis Mandel</strong></li><li><strong>Andrs Lopez</strong></li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>The concept</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Imagine arriving in a city like Paris or Mumbai and somebody is already waiting for you. Imagine that instead of going to eat at the place recommended by the guidebook, someone shows you their favorite restaurant. Imagine the experience staying as a personal guest of your new friend rather than sleeping in an impersonal hotel room.<strong>DirtyRoad</strong>makes it possible.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>How is it organised?</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Dreaming alone is not enough. That\'s why we have founded&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.bewelcome.org/wiki/BeVolunteer\">BeVolunteer</a>, a non-profit organisation registered in Rennes, France. Through BeVolunteer\'